e 20s.\nAt any rate, this is the only mes\nsage we could fathom in the account\nof Horace Vendig\u2019s rise to power by\nruthlessly crushing friend and foe,\nby coldly using the women who love\nhim. \u201cYou didn\u2019t kiss me, you\nkissed 48 per cent of Delta Power,\u201d\na wife he is discarding tells him.\nWhen Horace Anally meets his fate\nthe woman he couldn\u2019t get looks\nat his one friend and says, con\nsolingly. \"Vic he wasn't a man\nAMUSEMENTS _ j\nMV SMMK\nCROSBY\nWFOMTAINEJ\nfefjmperor\nUPM*ii^*\\ c<tor>y TECHNICOLOR\ntawiiiiiiiiiiM\nB MV SHIRK ooots fl\n1NCIR MADDEST, MERRIEST ADVENTURE!!\ni BUD ABBOTT I\nLOU COSTELLO\nmu EMU UON FKMS J[\nThe NOOSE\nHANGS HIGH'\nPaaiirlr With lw*.\nMMrr'i BraO\nlb (Nan Far Hr-in laWai\n\u25a0jfrffgltL\nrLA8T S 7...-COHBTK)N(ol\\\ndays cfufionri\n1332 /comi. AVt I\nI DOSTOYEVSKY'S MASTERPIECE I\n\\^aoc^r\\\nEnglish Titles\nI \"Bold and Exciting\". New Yorker\nI \"Gerald Philippe Sensational\"\nft N. Y. TIMES\nI MYRA HESS Ploys 1st Met.'\nll/fAa \"BEETHOVEN'S\n1^ APASSIONATA\" l\nhe was a way of life.\u201d This\ncan't be anything but an attack\non margin speculating.\nThere are a couple of moments\nwhen \u201cRuthless.'' is enlivened by\nSydney Greenstreet, but even Mr.\nGreenstxeet's shoulders are not\nbroad enough for this burden.\nDiana Lynn plays two girls and is\nunderstandably confused, iL o u i s\nHayward (also understandably)\nseems to be wishing he were some\nwhere else, and Zachary Scott rolls\nhis eyes and stares into space to in- j\nriicate how ruthless he is. He only!\nmanages to look silly, though, whieh:\ndoes not make him seem out of\nplace in \u201cRuthless.\u201d\n\nThe Capitol's stage show pre\nsents proof that ex-Govemors do\nnot have to retire asv elder states\nmen, go into the insurance business\nor run for Congress. They can, at\nleast ex-Governors of Louisiana can,\nget together hill-billy bands and\nAMUSEMENTS\nI' iffirfriif'tin\nI\nm dSp&frPk&ce sc*mm/\\\nS=1\nzapiaiy scon inns haywaro\nmm